Sass Values

=====================

Sass Basics :

1. Variables :

Contoh Code Buat index.html :

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>

<body>
    <H1>TEST</H1>
</body>

</html>

============================= FILE SASS : file nya styles.scss

SCSS SYNTAX
$font-stack: Helvetica, sans-serif;
$primary-color: #333;

body {
  font: 100% $font-stack;
  color: $primary-color;
}

==================================jangan lupa confert ke sass : 

1. sass styles.scss styles.css
2. save link css nya : <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">

=======================================

              ================     2. Number di SASS : ============================

=========================index .html nya 

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Title</h1>
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

============================== file sass nya styles.scss

$base-font-size: 16px;
$padding: 20px;
$opacity: 0.75;

.container {
  font-size: $base-font-size;
  padding: $padding;
  opacity: $opacity;
  
  width: $base-font-size * 2; // Perhitungan perkalian
  height: $base-font-size + $padding; // Perhitungan penjumlahan
}


================================================3. STRING PADA SASS :

index.html 

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>

<body>
    <header class="header">
        <h1 class="title"></h1>
    </header>
    <button class="button"></button>
</body>

</html>

=============================styles.scss.


$primary-color: "blue";
$secondary-color: "red";

$font-family: "Arial, sans-serif";
$font-size: 14px;

.header {
  color: $primary-color;
  font-family: $font-family;
}

.title {
  font-size: $font-size;
  content: "Welcome to our website!";
}

.button {
  background-color: $secondary-color;
  padding: 10px;
  text-align: center;

  &::before {
    content: "Click me";
  }
}


==================================================4. COLORING PADA SASS :

index.html 

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <h1 class="text-primary">Heading 1</h1>
  <h2 class="text-secondary">Heading 2</h2>
  <div class="background-primary">
    <p>Primary background color</p>
  </div>
  <div class="background-secondary">
    <p>Secondary background color</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

========================styles.scss.

$primary-color: #f00;
$secondary-color: #00f;

.text-primary {
  color: $primary-color;
}

.text-secondary {
  color: $secondary-color;
}

.background-primary {
  background-color: $primary-color;
}

.background-secondary {
  background-color: $secondary-color;
}

=========================================


SELANJUT NYA LIST CUMA KAGAK JALAN : sudah bisa 

index.html :

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <h1 class="primary-color">Heading 1</h1>
  <h2 class="secondary-color">Heading 2</h2>
  <p class="large-font-size">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.</p>
  <div class="medium-breakpoint">Breakpoint: Medium</div>
</body>
</html>

============================styles.scss.

$colors: red, green, blue;
$font-sizes: 12px, 14px, 16px;
$breakpoints: 480px, 768px, 1024px;

.primary-color {
  color: nth($colors, 1);
}

.secondary-color {
  color: nth($colors, 2);
}

.large-font-size {
  font-size: nth($font-sizes, 3);
}

.medium-breakpoint {
  @media (min-width: nth($breakpoints, 2)) {
    /* Gaya CSS untuk breakpoint medium */
  }
}


========================================
